These are Puzzles for 5x4 Level 1

.:: Puzzle 5x4-Level-1-1::.
There are 4 different favourite colors: brown, blood-red, light-blue, aquamarine
The people have 4 different hobbies: card-games, chess, skydiving, writing
The people perfer 4 different movie-genres: documentary, epic, family, romance
The people prefer 4 different music-genres: classical, d&b, dubstep, electronic
The people have 4 different jobs:  project-manager, designer, bartender, videographer
 1. the person watching documentary movies is on the right of the person who likes blood-red##1
 2. the person who's hobby is chess is on the right of the project-manager##1
 3. the person who's hobby is writing is on the left of the fan of d&b##1
 4. the designer is on the right of the project-manager##1
 5. the fan of classical is the person who likes brown##1
 6. the fan of d&b is on the left of the project-manager##1
 7. the fan of dubstep is on the right of the person who likes brown##1
 8. the person who likes light-blue is on the left of the person who's hobby is card-games##1
 9. the person watching family movies is the person who likes brown##1
10. the bartender is the person watching epic movies##1
11. the person who's hobby is card-games is on the right of the videographer##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |      2      |     3      |     4      |
| Color          | blood-red    | light-blue      | brown  | aquamarine     |
| Hobby         | writing    | skydiving   | card-games | chess      |
| Movie-Genre   | epic       | documentary | family     | romance    |
| Music-Genre   | electronic | d&b         | classical  | dubstep    |
| Job           | bartender      | videographer       | project-manager | designer |

