.:: Puzzle 5x4-Level-1-2::.
There are 4 different favourite colors: purple, lilac, chestnut, green
The people perfer 4 different movie-genres: documentary, drama, satire, spy
There are 4 different nationalities: mexican, polish, german, japanese
4 different pets are kept: ferret, hamster, pony, rat
The people prefer 4 different types of sport: cricket, handball, parkour, skiing
 1. the person watching drama movies is on the right of the person who's sport is cricket##1
 2. the mexican is on the right of the person who's sport is handball##1
 3. the person who's sport is skiing is on the right of the owner of the rat##1
 4. the person who likes green is on the far right##1
 5. the person who likes purple is on the right of the person who likes lilac##1
 6. the person who's sport is parkour is on the right of the person who likes chestnut##1
 7. the japanese is on the right of the person watching documentary movies##1
 8. the owner of the hamster is the japanese##1
 9. the person watching satire movies is the german##1
10. the mexican is on the far right##1
11. the person who likes chestnut is on the left of the owner of the ferret##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |      1      |    2    |    3     |       4       |
| Color      | lilac      | purple     | chestnut    | green |
| Movie-Genre   | documentary | drama   | satire   | spy           |
| Nationality   | polish  | japanese     | german    | mexican         |
| Pet           | rat         | hamster | pony     | ferret        |
| Sport         | cricket     | skiing  | handball | parkour       |

