.:: Puzzle 5x4-Level-1-3::.
There 4 different types of food: cabbage, cauliflower, grapes, lettuce
House: tower, futuristic, gothic-revival, cape-cod
4 different pets are kept: fish, frog, mouse, rabbit
The people have 4 different hobbies: chess, cooking, drawing, rock-climbing
The people use 4 different means of transport: bike, subway, tram, trike
 1. the person who's hobby is chess is on the far left##1
 2. the person who's hobby is cooking is on the right of the person driving the tram##1
 3. the person eating grapes is the owner of the rabbit##1
 4. the person eating cauliflower is on the right of the person driving the trike##1
 5. the person who's hobby is drawing is on the right of the person eating lettuce##1
 6. the person driving the trike is the person eating grapes##1
 7. the gothic-revival house is on the left of the person driving the trike##1
 8. the person driving the bike is on the right of the person driving the tram##1
 9. the cape-cod house is the owner of the frog##1
10. the futuristic house is on the left of the owner of the mouse##1
11. the person driving the trike is on the left of the owner of the mouse##1
12. the person eating grapes is on the right of the person who's hobby is cooking##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |      2       |    3    |       4       |
| Food          | cabbage    | lettuce      | grapes  | cauliflower   |
| House   | cape-cod     | gothic-revival      | futuristic | tower      |
| Pet           | frog       | fish         | rabbit  | mouse         |
| Hobby         | chess | cooking | drawing  | rock-climbing |
| Transport     | tram       | bike         | trike   | subway        |

