.:: Puzzle 5x4-Level-1-4::.
4 different games are played: snooker, scrabble, monopoly, canasta
The people prefer 4 different music-genres: reggae, trance, house, disco
There are 4 different nationalities: chinese, indonesian, japanese, thai
4 different pets are kept: cat, goat, guinea-pig, snake
The people use 4 different means of transport: jet-ski, roller, taxi, trike
 1. the owner of the goat is on the left of the owner of the cat##1
 2. the fan of disco is on the left of the person driving the roller##1
 3. the person driving the roller is on the right of the owner of the snake##1
 4. the owner of the guinea-pig is on the far right##1
 5. the person driving the jet-ski is on the far left##1
 6. the person driving the taxi is on the left of the person playing scrabble##1
 7. the thai is on the far right##1
 8. the fan of disco is on the right of the japanese##1
 9. the indonesian is on the left of the fan of reggae##1
10. the person playing snooker is on the far right##1
11. the person playing monopoly is on the far left##1
12. the person driving the trike is on the left of the fan of trance##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |    2     |     3     |     4      |
| Game      | monopoly   | canasta   | scrabble      | snooker     |
| Music-Genre          | house     | reggae   | disco | trance |
| Nationality   | indonesian | japanese | chinese   | thai       |
| Pet           | goat       | cat      | snake     | guinea-pig |
| Transport     | jet-ski    | taxi     | trike     | roller     |

