 7. the owner of the lizard is on the right of the person playing whist##1
 8. the owner of the snake is the person who likes grey##1
 9. the person eating pumpkin is the owner of the lizard##1
10. the person playing chess is on the left of the owner of the snake##1
11. the australian is on the right of the owner of the snake##1
12. the person who likes white is on the far left##1
13. the australian is on the right of the person playing go##1
14. the spanish is on the right of the turkish##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |     2     |     3      |    4     |
