There are 4 different nationalities: british, italian, mexican, pakistani
The people use 4 different means of transport: van, ship, motorbike, bus
 1. the person watching horror movies is on the right of the person driving the van##1
 2. the prince-smoker is on the left of the person watching epic movies##1
 3. the person watching family movies is the british##1
 4. the bolivar-smoker is on the right of the person driving the bus##1
 5. the person watching epic movies is the pakistani##1
 6. the person driving the bus is on the right of the davidoff-smoker##1
 7. the person driving the ship is on the right of the person watching horror movies##1
 8. the person watching family movies is on the right of the person eating apple##1
 9. the person driving the van is on the right of the mexican##1
10. the person watching family movies is on the left of the person eating eggplant##1
11. the person watching family movies is the person driving the van##1
12. the person eating watermelon is on the far right##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1     |     2      |     3     |      4       |
| Food          | apple     | strawberry | eggplant  | watermelon   |
| Cigar         | alhambra | davidoff    | prince | bolivar |
