.:: Puzzle 5x4-Level-1-18::.
There are 4 different favourite beverages: juice, mirinda, sprite, water
City: venice, edinburgh, liverpool, hannover
The people perfer 4 different movie-genres: disaster, mystery, thriller, western
The people grow 4 different varities of flowers: tulip, orchid, balloon-flower, daffodil
4 different pets are kept: cat, chinchilla, rat, snake
 1. the person who growsballoon-flower is on the far left##1
 2. the person drinking mirinda is the person watching western movies##1
 3. the person drinking sprite is on the left of the owner of the cat##1
 4. the person who growsdaffodil is on the left of the person who growstulip##1
 5. the person traveling to liverpool is the person drinking sprite##1
 6. the person traveling to hannover is the person drinking water##1
 7. the person traveling to edinburgh is on the right of the person watching mystery movies##1
 8. the person who growstulip is on the right of the owner of the snake##1
 9. the owner of the chinchilla is the person watching thriller movies##1
10. the person watching thriller movies is on the far left##1
11. the person drinking juice is on the right of the person drinking mirinda##1
12. the person traveling to hannover is on the left of the person watching mystery movies##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |      1      |      2      |      3       |    4     |
| Beverage      | water       | sprite      | mirinda      | juice    |
| City         | hannover | liverpool | edinburgh | venice  |
| Movie-Genre   | thriller    | mystery     | western      | disaster |
| Flower   | balloon-flower  | daffodil     | tulip    | orchid  |
| Pet           | chinchilla  | snake       | cat          | rat      |

