.:: Puzzle 5x4-Level-1-20::.
There 4 different types of food: apricot, asparagus, cherry, grapes
The people have 4 different hobbies: fishing, skydiving, sudoku, video-games
The people's birthday is in 4 different months: december, january, february, november
4 different pets are kept: cat, goat, goldfish, snake
There are 4 different favourite beverages: almond-milk, hot-chocolate, water, tea
 1. the person who's birthday is in november is the person who's hobby is fishing##1
 2. the owner of the goldfish is on the right of the person eating apricot##1
 3. the person who's birthday is in november is on the right of the person who's hobby is sudoku##1
 4. the person who's hobby is skydiving is on the left of the person who's birthday is in december##1
 5. the owner of the goldfish is the person who's hobby is video-games##1
 6. the person eating cherry is on the right of the person who's hobby is skydiving##1
 7. the person drinking hot-chocolate is on the right of the person who's birthday is in january##1
 8. the person who's birthday is in december is the person drinking almond-milk##1
 9. the person eating cherry is on the right of the owner of the goat##1
10. the person eating grapes is the owner of the snake##1
11. the owner of the snake is on the right of the person drinking water##1
12. the owner of the snake is on the left of the person who's birthday is in february##1

.:: Answer ::.
|             |      1       |       2       |       3        |      4      |
| Food        | asparagus    | grapes        | apricot        | cherry      |
| Hobby       | sudoku       | fishing       | skydiving      | video-games |
| Birthday         | january | november | february | december      |
| Pet         | cat          | snake         | goat           | goldfish    |
| Beverage   | water         | hot-chocolate       | tea     | almond-milk   |

 